name: 5D6-RA-7 (Fivedesix) (V)
Lore: 'Aide to Admiral Motti''s staff. Foul-tempered and vindictive. Feared by other droids. A spy for the ISB. Secretly investigates Imperial officers whose loyalties are in question.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. Power +1 while with your leader. If at a scomp link when opponent draws a destiny of: 1-3, you may activate one force; 4-6, you may draw top card of your reserve deck; 0 or 7 you may retrieve 1 force.',
